  <brief_title>Effect of Pioglitazone on Testosterone in Eugonadal Men With Type 2 Diabetes Mellitus - A Pilot Study</brief_title>
  <official_title>Effect of Pioglitazone on Testosterone in Eugonadal Men With Type 2 Diabetes Mellitus - A Pilot Study</official_title>
